title: Nero Ultra Edition 7.9
description:
Nero Burning ROM burns CDs and DVDs in the most important formats of the market: ISO, Joliet, Mixing Mode and others. Records CDs or DVDs using audio recording of the entire disc at one time or track by track. The software can duplicate discs and pre-master them, supporting the creation of covers and even an editor of audio files. All functions are easily accessible and ensure that tasks are completed quickly. Nero Burning ROM supports ISO 9660 images and ISO modes 1 and XA mode 2 for burning discs without temporary files. Also works with multi-session discs and mescalda recording modes, hybrid HFS, ISO / HFS, UDF, PSX, OFAS and more. The program also contains a edtior covers and resources to cover printing on CDs.
